@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5

actor User
entity Browser
participant CDN
participant "API Server" as API
database Database


User -> Browser ++ : navigate to page
Browser -> CDN : GET /page
CDN --> Browser : empty HTML shell + JS bundle
Browser -> Browser : parse and execute JavaScript
Browser --> User : display loading state (optional)

Browser -> API ++ : fetch data (JSON)
API -> Database : query data
Database --> API : data
API --> Browser -- : JSON response
Browser -> Browser : update UI with JavaScript
Browser --> User -- : display fully rendered page
@enduml
